thread.title: Graeme Johnstone

author: Graeme Johnstone
title: Graeme Johnstone
text: Imazing is a "must have" mobile accessory for anyone wanting to view/copy/backup photos or sms's.and other information on a mobile. The chat/email support that I needed when I had some initial questions was absolutely amazing. ( I'm someone that likes to understand the nuts and bolts ) If your after a reasonably priced, easy to use software interface to your mobile, this is the product to go for. Great work guys Graeme J.
